#

Mediterranean Chicken Gyros

35 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

High proteinMediterraneanLow carb

Cuisine:

MediterraneanGreek

Course:

MainLunchDinner

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthy

Description

Flavorful chicken wrapped in warm pita with fresh veggies and tangy tzatziki sauce.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 1 lb
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • dried oregano: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • pita bread: 4 pieces
  • cucumber: 1, diced
  • tomato: 1, diced
  • red onion: 1/2, thinly sliced
  • tzatziki sauce: 1 cup
